### Login as CUSTOMER (stores cookies in REST client session)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test.user@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

### Get customer profile (expected 200)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/profile

### Patch customer profile with valid payload (expected 200)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User Updated",
  "phone": "+966500000000",
  "countryCode": "SA",
  "city": "Riyadh",
  "addressLine1": "King Fahd Road",
  "postalCode": "11564",
  "preferredLanguage": "ar"
}

### Get customer profile again (expected updated values)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/profile

### Patch customer profile with invalid phone (expected 400)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "abc"
}

### Logout customer session
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/logout

### Get customer profile after logout (expected 401)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/profile

### Login as VENDOR-only account
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vendor.user@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

### Get customer profile as non-customer role (expected 403)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/profile
